<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.4.8">
<l>ciṟiyaṉeṉ ṟeṉṉiḷañ ciṅkattai yikaḻēl kaṇṭāy</l>
<l>ciṟumaiyiṉ vārttaiyai māvali yiṉiṭaic ceṉṟukēḷ</l>
<l>ciṟumaip piḻaikoḷḷil nīyumuṉ tēvaik kuriyaikāṇ</l>
<l>niṟaima tīneṭu mālvirain tuṉṉaik kūvukiṉṟāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Do not slight my young lion thinking, “he is small,” you see!</l>
<l>Go and ask Mahābali for news of [his] smallness.</l>
<l>And if you take his smallness as a fault, you are the owner of your own affairs, you see!</l>
<l>Tall Māl calls you, Full Moon, [come] quickly!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
